cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the security of IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of antenna arrays and physical-layer signatures also involves networking and communication technologies (cs.NI). The system design and implementation involve control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) to detect threats. The paper also discusses the optimization of energy consumption, which is related to information theory (cs.IT).
